column1: 2019/02/15 Statistics of Order Book & Trade per 5 Seconds
The volume and value of normal trading are included only.
The calculated amount of the overall market covers securities, funds, call warrants, put warrants and other securities.
One Trading Unit is 1,000 shares excluding offshore ETFs & secondary listing of foreign securities.
Information prior to 2011/01/16 is provided with the interval of every minute.
Information prior to 2014/02/23 is provided with the interval of every 15 seconds.
Information after 2014/02/24 is provided with the interval of every 10 seconds.
Information after 2014/12/29 is provided with the interval of every 5 seconds.
